-- EU Said to Sell 5.5 Million EU Carbon Permits at 6.55 Euros
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r o   V i t e l l i
-- 2012-12-13T14:04:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-13/eu-said-to-sell-5-5-million-eu-carbon-permits-at-6-55-euros.html
The European Union sold 5.5 million
spot carbon permits for 2013 at 6.55 euros a metric ton in an
auction on the European Energy Exchange AG, according to two
people with knowledge of the sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alessandro Vitelli in London at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Verdonck at 
 rverdonck@bloomberg.net  